				<wikidot:authorName>DrArmstrong</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>420092</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I generally downvote for animal death used for horror or shock value, but this article didn't do that. This cat <em>wanted</em> to expend all nine lives and efficiently did so in a way that was both funny and weird.</p> <p>+1</p> 
				 	]]>
